snippet: Top-seeded Rafael Nadal reached the semifinals of the Rio Open, showing no problems with a sore back in defeating Joao Sousa of Portugal 6-1, 6-0 on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Top-Seeded Nadal, No. 2 Ferrer Into Semifinals
headline.main: Top-Seeded Nadal, No. 2 Ferrer Into Semifinals

lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Rafael Nadal reached the semifinals of the Rio Open, showing no problems with a sore back in defeating Joao Sousa of Portugal 6-1, 6-0 on Friday.
